text: "D'yer Mak'er" () is a 1973 song by Led Zeppelin and taken from their fifth studio album Houses of the Holy. It went to number 20 in the United States and New Zealand and number 24 in Canada. ==References== Category:1973 songs Category:Led Zeppelin songs Category:Sheryl Crow songs Category:Reggae rock songs
title: D'yer Mak'er
